{"tid":2335132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友搞到我好煩","createTime":"2020-12-21T15:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T16:51:50.000Z","uid":350275,"like":4,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c36549914d385cf6c270cd8ff8d4176a4907f5","tid":2335132,"uid":350275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"同女朋友係埋一齊半年多啲，發現佢好奇怪。<br />\n同初初識既佢，同佢所講既自己完全係兩回事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如:<span class=\"large\">佢話自己個波有c，好中意做gym，點知一齊後半年(雖然撞正疫情)係屋企連基本拉筋都唔識，仲要俾我發現佢原來得b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n相處得得越嚟越唔舒服。有次我哋嘈交，我話想分開靜下，佢即刻話要打俾我屋企人講(佢有我屋企電話)，搞到我好大壓力。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">點解要搞我屋企人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"15b40d346dd89b1d5c9f6a5d5beab7a6da40c2f3","tid":2335132,"uid":9392,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"知你條女個波有C喇 網絡世界都要做假人借d意曬命<br />\n屌你老母臭西"},{"pid":"cd37d2c8824518672c28b4c57a5861be58d3c84c","tid":2335132,"uid":231957,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"港女係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n你而家先知？"},{"pid":"97e4e31b147061cb5aa5f7350c061b6f77d2a53a","tid":2335132,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:27:14.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63775bcb9ead50ae2ec3bf81058d25630e9cb94","tid":2335132,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"講者  我話我係蕭生個女<br />\n<br />\n你信唔信呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c04a2968e2106d8c56c2222f9c016d29317469","tid":2335132,"uid":3553,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"